thread.title: BRIEF-Partners Group To Sell Stake In Silicon Ranch Corporation To Shell

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Partners Group To Sell Stake In Silicon Ranch Corporation To Shell

organizations.name: brief-partners group to sell stake in silicon ranch corporation to shell

text:
Jan 15 (Reuters) - PARTNERS GROUP:
* PARTNERS GROUP TO SELL STAKE IN SILICON RANCH CORPORATION TO SHELL ‍
* ON BEHALF OF ITS CLIENTS, AGREED TO SELL ITS 43.83% OWNERSHIP STAKE IN SILICON RANCH CORPORATION​
* ‍SELLING ITS EQUITY STAKE TO SHELL FOR MINIMUM PROCEEDS OF USD 193 MILLION AND UP TO USD 217 MILLION​
* WILL CONTINUE TO SUPPORT SILICON RANCH THROUGH NEWLY ISSUED JUNIOR DEBT FINANCING SIMULTANEOUS WITH CLOSING OF SALE​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
